# .dockerignore
# Production practice: Exclude everything that shouldn't be in the Docker build context.
# Without this, Docker sends node_modules (100k+ files) to the daemon on every build.
# This makes builds dramatically faster and prevents secrets from leaking into images.

node_modules
dist
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
.git
.gitignore
README.md
*.log
.DS_Store
.vscode
PROJECT_GUIDE.txt
BEST_PRACTICES.txt
CONCEPTS_LEARNED.txt
